    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-06-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-06-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="426"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d426">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 811.304 M28/52.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 347.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-06-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 27, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The Department has received your No. 941 of the
                    19th instant, in which you report that the President of Cuba has issued a decree
                    directing a special demonstration of sympathy for the sailors of the Navy of the
                    United States who lost their lives in the explosion on the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Maine</hi>.</p>
                <pb facs="0421" n="305" xml:id="pg_305"/>
                <p>As suggested by yon, the Department desires you at the proper time to convey to
                    the Cuban Government an appropriate expression of the thanks of the Government
                    of the United States for this demonstration of sympathy.</p>
                <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">P. C. Knox</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
